{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SarTransmitterStatus"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SarTransmitterStatus\/sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCount"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh20SarTransmitterStatusV45sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCounts5UInt8Vvp","title":"sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCount","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCount"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SAR Unicast Retransmissions Without Progress Count state"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is a 4-bit value that controls the maximum number of transmissions of segments","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of segmented messages to a Unicast destination without progress","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(i.e., without newly marking any segment as acknowledged).","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCount"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The maximum number of transmissions of a segment without progress is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text"